item.title: GNOME Zazzle Store Sale
item.description: Tomorrow is the last day to save 17.76% at the GNOME Zazzle store. Zazzle is having a sale to celebrate Independence Day here in America. GUADEC is coming so now is a great time to place your order and have some cool gear to show off to all your GNOME friends in The Hague!
